; Survex entry whose *include target does not exist on disk. The
; scanner resolves the entry itself and emits a "missing *include
; target" warning without failing - the attach dialog's
; yellow-warning-but-[Attach]-enabled path (Phase 2 q18).
*begin MissingInclude
*fix A1 0 0 0
*data normal from to tape compass clino
A1 A2 5.0 0 0
*include "not_on_disk.svx"
*end MissingInclude
